{%- comment -%}
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
COUNTDOWN BANNER CAROUSEL (custom vcollect)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Custom addition to the Impact theme. Not part of Maestrooo's base code, so it lives in its own section file and can be
deleted without touching anything the theme ships.

Built for the 30 ans Pokémon and M6 drops, but nothing here is specific to them: each slide carries its own deadline,
wording, image and colors, so the same section serves the next launches.

********************************************
One slide per launch, rotating
********************************************

Slides are blocks, and they rotate inside Impact's own <slideshow-carousel>, the same element the theme's Slideshow
section uses. Reusing it rather than writing a second carousel means the arrows, dots, swipe gestures, autoplay and
fade transitions all behave exactly like the rest of the store, and keep working when Impact updates its script.

********************************************
The banner works without JavaScript
********************************************

Liquid computes the remaining days, hours and minutes and prints them. assets/custom-countdown.js only takes over to
keep them ticking. A shopper who never receives the script still sees how far away the drop is, which is why the numbers
are rendered server side rather than left at zero.

The deadline is emitted as a full ISO instant resolved in the shop timezone, so every visitor counts down to the same
moment whatever their own timezone.

********************************************
Slides remove themselves
********************************************

Once a deadline has passed the slide drops out of the carousel on its own if "masquer après la date" is on, so a launch
never lingers on the homepage announcing an event that already happened. When the last slide expires the whole section
disappears. A slide whose date is empty or unreadable is never hidden: an unparseable date must not silently erase
content the merchant entered.
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- comment -%}
  Count the slides that survive their deadline, and remember the first of them: the carousel colors its controls from
  the selected slide, so the section has to start on the colors of the slide actually shown first, not on those of a
  block that expired days ago.
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- liquid
  assign now_timestamp = 'now' | date: '%s' | plus: 0
  assign visible_count = 0

  for block in section.blocks
    assign block_target = block.settings.target_date | date: '%s' | plus: 0
    assign block_remaining = block_target | minus: now_timestamp

    if block_target > 0 and block_remaining <= 0 and block.settings.hide_when_expired
      continue
    endif

    assign visible_count = visible_count | plus: 1

    if visible_count == 1
      assign first_block = block
    endif
  endfor
-%}

{%- if visible_count > 0 -%}
  <script type="module" src="{{ 'custom-countdown.js' | asset_url }}"></script>

  <style>
    {%- if section.settings.controls_type == 'filled_arrows' -%}
      {%- assign controls_background = first_block.settings.button_background -%}
      {%- assign controls_color = first_block.settings.button_text_color -%}
    {%- else -%}
      {%- assign controls_color = first_block.settings.text_color -%}
    {%- endif -%}

    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} {
      --slideshow-background: {{ first_block.settings.background_gradient | default: first_block.settings.background }};
      --slideshow-controls-background: {{ controls_background.rgb }};
      --slideshow-controls-color: {{ controls_color.rgb }};

      {%- if section.settings.allow_transparent_header -%}
        margin-block-start: calc(-1 * var(--header-height) * var(--section-is-first));
      {%- endif -%}
    }

    {%- comment -%}
      The theme applies --content-over-media-height to the image, not to the container, so a slide running on a gradient
      alone would collapse to the height of its text. Mirroring it as a minimum keeps the hero the size the merchant
      picked whether or not an image has been uploaded.
    {%- endcomment -%}
    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .content-over-media {
      min-block-size: var(--content-over-media-height, auto);
    }

    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .countdown {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: var(--spacing-4);
      margin-block: var(--spacing-4);
    }

    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .countdown__unit {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      min-width: 4.5rem;
      padding: var(--spacing-2) var(--spacing-3);
      border-radius: var(--rounded-sm);
    }

    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .countdown__value {
      font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 5vw, 3rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.1;
      font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    }

    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .countdown__label {
      font-size: var(--text-xs);
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      opacity: 0.75;
    }

    {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
      {%- if section.settings.controls_type == 'filled_arrows' -%}
        {%- assign controls_background = block.settings.button_background -%}
        {%- assign controls_color = block.settings.button_text_color -%}
      {%- else -%}
        {%- assign controls_color = block.settings.text_color -%}
      {%- endif -%}

      #block-{{ block.id }} {
        --slideshow-slide-background: {{ block.settings.background_gradient | default: block.settings.background }};
        --slideshow-slide-controls-background: {{ controls_background.rgb }};
        --slideshow-slide-controls-color: {{ controls_color.rgb }};
      }

      #block-{{ block.id }} .countdown__unit {
        background: rgb({{ block.settings.countdown_background.rgb }} / {{ block.settings.countdown_opacity | divided_by: 100.0 }});
        color: {{ block.settings.countdown_text_color }};
      }
    {%- endfor -%}
  </style>

  {%- assign carousel_id = 'countdown-banners-' | append: section.id -%}

  <x-slideshow class="slideshow {% unless section.settings.full_width %}slideshow--boxed{% endunless %} {% if visible_count > 1 %}slideshow--multiple-slides{% endif %}" {% if section.settings.allow_transparent_header %}allow-transparent-header{% endif %}>
    {%- unless section.settings.full_width -%}
      <span class="slideshow__slide-background"></span>
    {%- endunless -%}

    <slideshow-carousel id="{{ carousel_id }}" class="slideshow__carousel" reveal-on-scroll="true" selector=".slideshow__slide" transition="{{ section.settings.transition_type }}" {% if section.settings.autoplay and visible_count > 1 %}autoplay="{{ section.settings.cycle_speed }}"{% endif %} role="region">
      {%- assign rendered_count = 0 -%}

      {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
        {%- liquid
          assign target_timestamp = block.settings.target_date | date: '%s' | plus: 0
          assign remaining = target_timestamp | minus: now_timestamp
          assign is_expired = false

          comment
            A blank or unreadable date leaves nothing to count down to, and must never make the slide disappear.
          endcomment
          if target_timestamp == 0
            assign remaining = 0
          elsif remaining <= 0
            assign remaining = 0
            assign is_expired = true
          endif
        -%}

        {%- if is_expired and block.settings.hide_when_expired -%}
          {%- continue -%}
        {%- endif -%}

        {%- liquid
          assign remaining_days = remaining | divided_by: 86400
          assign remaining_hours = remaining | modulo: 86400 | divided_by: 3600
          assign remaining_minutes = remaining | modulo: 3600 | divided_by: 60
          assign remaining_seconds = remaining | modulo: 60

          assign rendered_count = rendered_count | plus: 1
          assign is_first = false

          if rendered_count == 1
            assign is_first = true
          endif
        -%}

        {%- capture slide_style -%}--content-over-media-overlay: {{ block.settings.overlay_color.rgb }} / {{ block.settings.overlay_opacity | divided_by: 100.0 }};{%- endcapture -%}
        {%- capture slide_class -%}content-over-media content-over-media--{{ section.settings.image_size }} {% unless section.settings.full_width %}rounded{% endunless %}{%- endcapture -%}

        <div id="block-{{ block.id }}" class="slideshow__slide {% if is_first %}is-selected{% endif %}" role="group" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
          <div {% render 'surface', class: slide_class, style: slide_style, background: block.settings.background, background_gradient: block.settings.background_gradient, text_color: block.settings.text_color %}>
            {%- comment -%}---------------- MEDIA ----------------{%- endcomment -%}
            {%- if block.settings.image != blank -%}
              {%- capture sizes -%}{% if section.settings.full_width %}100vw{% else %}min({{ settings.page_width }}px, 100vw){% endif %}{%- endcapture -%}
              {%- capture loading_strategy -%}{% if is_first %}eager{% else %}lazy{% endif %}{%- endcapture -%}
              {%- capture fetch_priority -%}{% if is_first %}high{% else %}low{% endif %}{%- endcapture -%}
              {%- capture image_class -%}{% if block.settings.mobile_image != blank %}hidden sm:block{% endif %}{%- endcapture -%}

              {{- block.settings.image | image_url: width: block.settings.image.width | image_tag: loading: loading_strategy, fetchpriority: fetch_priority, sizes: sizes, widths: '400,600,800,1000,1200,1400,1600,1800,2000,2400,2800,3200', class: image_class -}}

              {%- if block.settings.mobile_image != blank -%}
                {{- block.settings.mobile_image | image_url: width: block.settings.mobile_image.width | image_tag: loading: loading_strategy, fetchpriority: fetch_priority, sizes: sizes, widths: '400,600,800,1000,1200,1400,1600', class: 'sm:hidden' -}}
              {%- endif -%}
            {%- endif -%}

            {%- comment -%}---------------- CONTENT ----------------{%- endcomment -%}
            <div class="{{ block.settings.mobile_text_position }} {{ block.settings.desktop_text_position }}">
              <div class="prose">
                {%- if block.settings.subheading != blank -%}
                  <p class="bold" data-sequence="subheading">{{ block.settings.subheading | escape }}</p>
                {%- endif -%}

                {%- if block.settings.title != blank -%}
                  <p class="{{ block.settings.heading_tag }}" data-sequence="heading">
                    {%- render 'styled-text', content: block.settings.title, apparition_effect: true -%}
                  </p>
                {%- endif -%}

                {%- if block.settings.content != blank -%}
                  <div>{{ block.settings.content }}</div>
                {%- endif -%}

                {%- if block.settings.show_countdown -%}
                  <countdown-timer class="countdown" target="{{ block.settings.target_date | date: '%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%S%z' }}" {% if is_expired %}expired{% endif %}>
                    <span class="countdown__unit">
                      <span class="countdown__value" data-countdown-days>{{ remaining_days }}</span>
                      <span class="countdown__label">{{ 'general.countdown.days' | t }}</span>
                    </span>
                    <span class="countdown__unit">
                      <span class="countdown__value" data-countdown-hours>{{ remaining_hours }}</span>
                      <span class="countdown__label">{{ 'general.countdown.hours' | t }}</span>
                    </span>
                    <span class="countdown__unit">
                      <span class="countdown__value" data-countdown-minutes>{{ remaining_minutes }}</span>
                      <span class="countdown__label">{{ 'general.countdown.minutes' | t }}</span>
                    </span>
                    <span class="countdown__unit">
                      <span class="countdown__value" data-countdown-seconds>{{ remaining_seconds }}</span>
                      <span class="countdown__label">{{ 'general.countdown.seconds' | t }}</span>
                    </span>
                  </countdown-timer>
                {%- endif -%}

                {%- if block.settings.button_text != blank -%}
                  {%- render 'button', content: block.settings.button_text, href: block.settings.button_url, size: 'lg', background: block.settings.button_background, text_color: block.settings.button_text_color -%}
                {%- endif -%}
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      {%- endfor -%}

      {%- if visible_count > 1 and section.settings.controls_type != 'none' -%}
        <div class="slideshow__controls">
          {%- case section.settings.controls_type -%}
            {%- when 'filled_arrows' or 'outline_arrows' -%}
              <div class="prev-next-buttons">
                <button is="prev-button" aria-controls="{{ carousel_id }}" class="circle-button circle-button--lg {% if section.settings.controls_type == 'filled_arrows' %}circle-button--fill{% else %}circle-button--bordered{% endif %} group">
                  <span class="sr-only">{{ 'general.accessibility.previous' | t }}</span>
                  <span class="animated-arrow animated-arrow--reverse"></span>
                </button>

                <button is="next-button" aria-controls="{{ carousel_id }}" class="circle-button circle-button--lg {% if section.settings.controls_type == 'filled_arrows' %}circle-button--fill{% else %}circle-button--bordered{% endif %} group">
                  <span class="sr-only">{{ 'general.accessibility.next' | t }}</span>
                  <span class="animated-arrow"></span>
                </button>
              </div>

            {%- when 'numbers' -%}
              <page-dots class="numbered-dots" aria-controls="{{ carousel_id }}">
                {%- for i in (1..visible_count) -%}
                  <button type="button" class="numbered-dots__item" aria-current="{% if forloop.first %}true{% else %}false{% endif %}">
                    <svg width="100%" height="100%" {% if section.settings.autoplay %}style="--percent: 0"{% endif %}>
                      <circle cx="50%" cy="50%" r="15"></circle>
                      <circle cx="50%" cy="50%" r="15"></circle>
                    </svg>

                    <span>{{- forloop.index -}}</span>
                  </button>
                {%- endfor -%}
              </page-dots>

            {%- when 'dots' -%}
              <page-dots class="stretching-dots" aria-controls="{{ carousel_id }}">
                {%- for i in (1..visible_count) -%}
                  <button type="button" class="tap-area" aria-current="{% if forloop.first %}true{% else %}false{% endif %}">
                    <span class="sr-only">{{ 'general.accessibility.go_to_item' | t: index: forloop.index }}</span>
                  </button>
                {%- endfor -%}
              </page-dots>
          {%- endcase -%}
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}
    </slideshow-carousel>
  </x-slideshow>
{%- endif -%}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Carrousel de bannières",
  "class": "shopify-section--slideshow",
  "tag": "section",
  "disabled_on": {
    "templates": ["password"],
    "groups": ["header", "custom.overlay"]
  },
  "max_blocks": 5,
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "full_width",
      "label": "Pleine largeur",
      "default": true
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "allow_transparent_header",
      "label": "Autoriser l'en-tête transparent",
      "info": "Ne s'applique que si cette section est la première de la page.",
      "default": true
    },
    {
      "type": "select",
      "id": "image_size",
      "label": "Hauteur",
      "options": [
        {
          "value": "sm",
          "label": "Petite"
        },
        {
          "value": "md",
          "label": "Moyenne"
        },
        {
          "value": "lg",
          "label": "Grande"
        },
        {
          "value": "auto",
          "label": "Automatique"
        }
      ],
      "default": "md"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Défilement"
    },
    {
      "type": "select",
      "id": "controls_type",
      "label": "Contrôles",
      "options": [
        {
          "value": "none",
          "label": "Aucun"
        },
        {
          "value": "filled_arrows",
          "label": "Flèches pleines"
        },
        {
          "value": "outline_arrows",
          "label": "Flèches contournées"
        },
        {
          "value": "numbers",
          "label": "Numéros"
        },
        {
          "value": "dots",
          "label": "Points"
        }
      ],
      "default": "dots"
    },
    {
      "type": "select",
      "id": "transition_type",
      "label": "Type de transition",
      "options": [
        {
          "value": "fade",
          "label": "Fondu"
        },
        {
          "value": "fade_with_text",
          "label": "Fondu avec animation du texte"
        }
      ],
      "default": "fade_with_text"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "autoplay",
      "label": "Faire défiler automatiquement",
      "default": true
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "cycle_speed",
      "min": 4,
      "max": 20,
      "step": 1,
      "unit": "sec",
      "label": "Changer de bannière toutes les",
      "default": 6
    }
  ],
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "banner",
      "name": "Bannière",
      "settings": [
        {
          "type": "image_picker",
          "id": "image",
          "label": "Image (ordinateur)"
        },
        {
          "type": "image_picker",
          "id": "mobile_image",
          "label": "Image (mobile)"
        },
        {
          "type": "header",
          "content": "Compte à rebours"
        },
        {
          "type": "checkbox",
          "id": "show_countdown",
          "label": "Afficher le compte à rebours",
          "default": true
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "target_date",
          "label": "Date visée",
          "info": "Au format AAAA-MM-JJ, par exemple 2026-09-16. Une heure peut être ajoutée : 2026-09-16 10:00.",
          "default": "2026-09-16"
        },
        {
          "type": "checkbox",
          "id": "hide_when_expired",
          "label": "Masquer la bannière une fois la date passée",
          "default": true
        },
        {
          "type": "header",
          "content": "Contenu"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "subheading",
          "label": "Sur-titre",
          "default": "SORTIE MONDIALE"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "title",
          "label": "Titre",
          "default": "30 ANS POKÉMON"
        },
        {
          "type": "select",
          "id": "heading_tag",
          "label": "Taille du titre",
          "options": [
            {
              "value": "h0",
              "label": "Très grande"
            },
            {
              "value": "h1",
              "label": "Grande"
            },
            {
              "value": "h2",
              "label": "Moyenne"
            }
          ],
          "default": "h0"
        },
        {
          "type": "richtext",
          "id": "content",
          "label": "Texte"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "button_text",
          "label": "Texte du bouton",
          "default": "Découvrir la gamme"
        },
        {
          "type": "url",
          "id": "button_url",
          "label": "Lien du bouton"
        },
        {
          "type": "select",
          "id": "mobile_text_position",
          "label": "Position du texte (mobile)",
          "options": [
            {
              "value": "place-self-center text-center",
              "label": "Centre"
            },
            {
              "value": "place-self-end-center text-center",
              "label": "Bas"
            }
          ],
          "default": "place-self-center text-center"
        },
        {
          "type": "select",
          "id": "desktop_text_position",
          "label": "Position du texte (ordinateur)",
          "options": [
            {
              "value": "sm:place-self-center sm:text-center",
              "label": "Centre"
            },
            {
              "value": "sm:place-self-center-start sm:text-start",
              "label": "Gauche"
            },
            {
              "value": "sm:place-self-end-center sm:text-center",
              "label": "Bas"
            }
          ],
          "default": "sm:place-self-center sm:text-center"
        },
        {
          "type": "header",
          "content": "Couleurs",
          "info": "Le dégradé remplace la couleur unie quand il est renseigné."
        },
        {
          "type": "color",
          "id": "background",
          "label": "Fond",
          "default": "#1a1a1a"
        },
        {
          "type": "color_background",
          "id": "background_gradient",
          "label": "Dégradé de fond",
          "default": "linear-gradient(140deg, rgba(26, 26, 26, 1), rgba(0, 58, 112, 1) 100%)"
        },
        {
          "type": "color",
          "id": "text_color",
          "label": "Texte",
          "default": "#ffffff"
        },
        {
          "type": "color",
          "id": "overlay_color",
          "label": "Voile sur l'image",
          "default": "#000000"
        },
        {
          "type": "range",
          "id": "overlay_opacity",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 100,
          "step": 1,
          "unit": "%",
          "label": "Opacité du voile",
          "default": 40
        },
        {
          "type": "color",
          "id": "countdown_background",
          "label": "Fond des compteurs",
          "default": "#ffffff"
        },
        {
          "type": "range",
          "id": "countdown_opacity",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 100,
          "step": 5,
          "unit": "%",
          "label": "Opacité des compteurs",
          "default": 15
        },
        {
          "type": "color",
          "id": "countdown_text_color",
          "label": "Texte des compteurs",
          "default": "#ffffff"
        },
        {
          "type": "color",
          "id": "button_background",
          "label": "Fond du bouton",
          "default": "#002d78"
        },
        {
          "type": "color",
          "id": "button_text_color",
          "label": "Texte du bouton",
          "default": "#ffffff"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Carrousel de bannières",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "banner"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
